videos.headline: Moore throws 40-yard strike to Pinckney
videos.description: Cincinnati QB Hayden Moore connects with  wide receiver JJ Pinckney for a 40-yard gain in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Cincinnati's gadget play goes for 33 yards
videos.description: The Bearcats' offense dives into its bag of tricks, running a double-reverse pass that goes for a 33-yard gain.

videos.headline: Banks keeps it himself for TD
videos.description: Tulane QB Jonathan Banks takes the keeper 53 yards to the end zone to give the Green Wave the lead in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Cincinnati's Moore finds Gray for TD
videos.description: Bearcats QB Hayden Moore finds Devin Gray in stride for a 39-yard score to give Cincinnati the lead.

videos.headline: Cincinnati's Boone pounds his way in for TD
videos.description: Mike Boone bullies his way into the end zone with a great second effort to give the Bearcats the lead in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Cincinnati's Doaks seals the game with 1st down
videos.description: Gerrid Doaks puts the game away for the Bearcats sprinting 57-yards for a first down late in the fourth quarter.
